Setup

  $ export SHEET_FILE=$CRAMTMP/sheet-tag
  $ alias tt="tt --no-color"

When not working

  $ tt tag a-tag
  For all I know, you aren't working on anything. I don't know what to do.
  See `tt -h` to know how to start working.
  [1]

Not giving a tag to add

  $ tt on something
  Start working on something.
  $ tt tag
  Please provide at least one tag to add.
  [1]
